769
00:36:12.875 --> 00:36:15.795
that animals are able to experience the world subjectively

770
00:36:16.065 --> 00:36:18.835
have emulsions and experience pain and pleasure.

771
00:36:19.255 --> 00:36:22.195
We recommend that emergency management legislation reflect

772
00:36:22.195 --> 00:36:23.275
that same principle.

773
00:36:23.825 --> 00:36:26.955
This is not about elevating animals above people.

774
00:36:27.245 --> 00:36:29.355
Human safety must always come first.

775
