00:36:35.745 --> 00:36:38.095
We're asking that responders are given clear powers

778
00:36:38.095 --> 00:36:40.335
to actively cease transport, shelter,

779
00:36:40.395 --> 00:36:43.495
and provide care for animals wherever possible without

780
00:36:43.495 --> 00:36:45.415
having to make contact with the owner First.

